@NODE "Introduction" "Introduction"

 @{b}Introduction@{ub}
 MUIReaderX is an offline message reader/writer for Xenolink BBS Systems. MUIReaderX is a GUI to Xenolink's message base and can be compared with programms like Spot and Foozle. With MUIReaderX you can do all
the basic message handlings plus more.

 @{b}Features@{ub}
 - Its Fast (but it can be faster ;)
 - Private MailBox
 - Supports UUCP gateways like XUUCP
 - Private UserList
 - Definable Text Strings (per sections)
 - Notifies you when you have NEW waitingmail
 - Uses MemoryPools
 - UUDecode & UnMime.
 - Arexx
 - Uses MUI ;)
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Requirements" "Requirements"

 @{b}Hardware Requirements@{ub}
 - Amiga Computer with a minimum of 1MB RAM free

 @{b}Needed Software@{ub}
 - AmigaDOS v2.04 (v37) or higher
 - Xenolink BBS v1.984 or higher
 - MUI v3.3 or higher
 - MCCMailtext v1.0 or higher (included)
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Registering" "Registering"

 @{b}Registering@{ub}
 MUIUploaderX is called 'XenoWare'; that means that @{i}ONLY@{ui} Registerd Xenolink Sysops are allowed to use this product. There are two versions of MUIReaderX, an unregistered and registered version. The difference is only noticable in the About window and Tearline. Both versions are 100% identical in functionality.

 @{u}Unregistered Version:@{uu}
  Tearline     : --- Xenolink vx.xx, MUIReaderX vx.xx [Unreg]
  About Window : ** Unregistered Version **

 @{u}Registered Version:@{uu}
  Tearline     : --- Xenolink vx.xx, MUIReaderX vx.xx [#12]
  About Window : Robin Vermaat
                 Hoogbuurlostraat 27
                 2573 HV, Den Haag


 The registration fee is something that you (the sysop) may determin. You can pay me nothing and happily use the unregisterd version or fill in the @{"registration form" link "Registration/MAIN"} and send me an x amount of guilders or deutchmarks. If you decide to register you will receive a private keyfile (through email or crash netmail).

 @{u}Registrations are welcome at:@{uu}
    Robin Vermaat
    Hoogbuurlostraat 27              
    2573 HV, Den Haag
    Netherlands
    Giro: 7144908

 @{i}NOTE: Please only send mony in FL (Dutch Guilders) or DM (Deutch Marks). I prefer FL (Dutch Guilders)@{ui}

@ENDNODE

