     * Private MailBox (Xenolink User Directory)

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: None@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Iconify" "Project/Iconify"

  @{b}Project/Iconify@{ub}
  This menu option iconifies the application. If the application is iconified and a new message arrives the NewMail icon will appear on the workbench screen.

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: RAMIGA I@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "CheckMail" "Project/CheckMail"

  @{b}Project/CheckMail@{ub}
  This menu option checks if there is new waitingmail. This menu option is obsolete because MUIReaderX will notify automaticly when a new messsage arrives.

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: None@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "About" "Project/About"

  @{b}Project/About@{ub}
