  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: RAMIGA ?@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "AboutMUI" "Project/About MUI"

  @{b}Project/About MUI@{ub}
  This menu option shows the about MUI window.

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: None@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Quit" "Project/Quit"

  @{b}Project/Quit@{ub}
  This menu option Quits MUIReaderX.

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: RAMIGA Q@{uu}
@ENDNODE

