@NODE "Write" "Messages/Write"

  @{b}Messages/Write@{ub}
  This menu option writes a new message in current section. After you have written and saved your message in your defined editor. You can fill in the details of your message in the @{"Message Header Window" link "Header"}.

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: RAMIGA W@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Reply" "Messages/Reply"

  @{b}Messages/Reply@{ub}
  This menu option reply on the message you were currenly reading. After you have written and saved your reply message in your defined editor. You can fill in the details of your message in the @{"Message Header Window" link "Header"}.

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: RAMIGA R@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "CrossReply" "Messages/CrossReply"

  @{b}Messages/CrossReply@{ub}
  Same as Reply but destination section is now selectable. For example, you may wish to Netmail reply to a message you have seen in an echomail section. 

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: RAMIGA C@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Forward" "Messages/Forward"

  @{b}Messages/Forward@{ub}
  This menu option forwards the current message to any section. The forwarded message will contain the original message data as part of the message, showing from what section the original came, from whom, and when etc.

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: RAMIGA F@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "CatchupCurrent" "Messages/Catchup Current"

  @{b}Messages/Catchup Current@{ub}
   You can activate the Catchup Current from the Messages menu. This will catchup only the current section

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: None@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "CatchupAll" "Messages/Catchup All"

  @{b}Messages/Catchup All@{ub}
   You can activate the Catchup Current from the Messages menu. This will catchup ALL sections know to Xenolink.

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: None@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Save" "Messages/Save"

  @{b}Messages/Save@{ub}
  This menu option exports current message to disk as an ASCII file.

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: RAMIGA S@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Delete" "Messages/Delete"

  @{b}Messages/Delete@{ub}
  This menu option delete's current message from the Xenolink Message Base.

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: RAMIGA D@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "AddToMailbox" "Messages/Add To Mailbox"

  @{b}Messages/Add To Mailbox@{ub}
  This menu option add's current message to your mailbox.

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: RAMIGA =@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "AddToUserList" "Messages/Add To UserList"

  @{b}Messages/Add To UserList@{ub}
  This menu option add's the FROM: user of current message to your user database.

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: RAMIGA +@{uu}
@ENDNODE

