  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: None@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Save Users" "Preferences/Save Users"

  @{b}Preferences/Save Users@{ub}
  This menu option saves the User DataBase to your Xenolink User Directory, eq (XUSERS:Robin_Vermaar/MUIReaderX.users)

  @{u}Keyboard short-cut: None@{uu}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Save Settings" "Preferences/Save Settings"

  @{b}Preferences/Save Settings@{ub}
